<body>
    <h1>Getting Started with Mews Automations</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"0f191f205c4c">
<style>[data-colorid=3Dk29o33w8yi]{color:#006644} html[data-color-mode=3Dda=
rk] [data-colorid=3Dk29o33w8yi]{color:#99ffdd}</style>Mews Automations allo=
w you to build no-code workflows that react to events in your property and =
perform actions automatically =E2=80=94 saving your team time and ensuring =
nothing falls through the cracks. Think of it as your personal assistant th=
at watches for things happening in Mews and takes action on your behalf, 24=
/7.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f94fd7c2d734">Whether you want to automatically upgrade room=
s for loyal guests, send a welcome SMS, assign tasks to your team, or add p=
roducts to reservations =E2=80=94 Automations make it possible without writ=
ing a single line of code.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f9f513f38eff"><strong>In this guide</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"72f99fd3-523c-46c5-9fe4-b81fbe122ea4">
<li local-id=3D"00018593-5be3-4f65-aba9-53107e360d01">
