ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#1.-What-Are-A=
utomations%3F" rel=3D"nofollow">1. What are Automations?</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc179979-d3af-40fc-a818-0d28ce311bb1">
<p local-id=3D"e186da7b005f"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#2.-Key-Concep=
ts" rel=3D"nofollow">2. Key concepts</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9917f9f8-9374-4486-b0a5-70f761e93389">
<p local-id=3D"a20caa147568"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#3.-Accessing-=
