<p local-id=3D"81a6ab7c9a44"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#6.-The-Flow-D=
esigner-(Canvas)" rel=3D"nofollow">6. The flow designer (canvas)</a></p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"e4bf1916-5bfe-493d-8fe7-57f54a382109">
<p local-id=3D"7f4f57de1167"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#7.-Adding-Com=
ponents-to-the-Canvas" rel=3D"nofollow">7. Adding components to the canvas<=
/a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d1027d27-faa0-46ef-b9ae-335133f3561c">
<p local-id=3D"04da7969ea74"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#8.-Connecting=
-Components" rel=3D"nofollow">8. Connecting components</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f8553a3-87b1-4030-9571-5091b8dab1fb">
<p local-id=3D"e82ebf4d11ea"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#9.-Configurin=
g-Components-(the-Inspector)" rel=3D"nofollow">9. Configuring components (t=
he Inspector)</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfce34db-53ce-46db-bc09-691ecb3b7b19">
<p local-id=3D"7d62f3a93517"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#10.-Using-Var=
iables-from-Previous-Components" rel=3D"nofollow">10. Using variables from =
previous components</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"08418fe0-f59d-43e9-991e-59e4f26fca78">
<p local-id=3D"b8c139e45828"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#11.-Modifiers=
-%E2%80%94-Transforming-Data" rel=3D"nofollow">11. Modifiers =E2=80=94 tran=
sforming data</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"99d069bb-8500-4920-95b4-cbb861163f91">
<p local-id=3D"dc91900956bf"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#12.-Mews-Comp=
onents-Overview" rel=3D"nofollow">12. Mews components overview</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"26614164-7d25-488c-b276-7eb7fc861ac5">
<p local-id=3D"dc1c9fa2ddad"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#13.-Built-in-=
Utility-Components" rel=3D"nofollow">13. Built-in utility components</a></p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"fdbffc0e-dcf5-4087-9043-d1b79d6ba09d">
<p local-id=3D"7b792b21c43b"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#14.-Starting%=
2C-Stopping%2C-and-Testing-Your-Automation" rel=3D"nofollow">14. Starting, =
stopping, and testing your automation</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"db792543-692f-4590-9344-bae62c9aace3">
<p local-id=3D"883e576a1625"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#15.-The-Actio=
n-Log" rel=3D"nofollow">15. The Action Log</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"55114b3c-0f14-4e61-b20b-a6e3917d9b22">
<p local-id=3D"21a105e40dd1"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#16.-Using-Tem=
plates" rel=3D"nofollow">16. Using templates</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"04461f4c-af95-44e1-ac49-6b2561140322">
<p local-id=3D"bb9ab5c20c38"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#17.-Best-Prac=
tices" rel=3D"nofollow">17. Best practices</a></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d3cba6cd-0110-4188-bad0-8fee6f41522d">
<p local-id=3D"fbd1f027448b"><a href=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spa=
ces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Started+with+Mews+Automations#18.-Troublesh=
ooting" rel=3D"nofollow">18. Troubleshooting</a></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c8428e33-3071-41dc-bb60-575f97fef560">
<h2 local-id=3D"cadab2331613" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-1.Wha=
tAreAutomations?">1. What Are Automations?</h2>
<p local-id=3D"456f0edf7c6c">Automations are visual workflows that connect =
<strong>triggers</strong> (events that start the workflow) with <strong>act=
ions</strong> (tasks that are performed automatically). They follow a simpl=
e logic:</p>
<p local-id=3D"42bcf8179820"><strong>When</strong> something happens (a tri=
gger) =E2=86=92 <strong>Then</strong> do something (one or more actions)</p=
>
<p local-id=3D"5ac5fb3b947a">For example:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2b312b47-c88d-480f-a530-fa4a15c41f87">
<li local-id=3D"3408a308-7e44-4cab-a08d-ae6f68112f60">
<p local-id=3D"1bacf52c4467"><strong>When</strong> a guest checks in =E2=86=
=92 <strong>Then</strong> send them a welcome SMS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f044c68c-cc41-4a41-a935-dab1ca3733f9">
<p local-id=3D"f5d592d6de3a"><strong>When</strong> it's 9 AM every day =E2=
=86=92 <strong>Then</strong> check today's arrivals, find loyalty members, =
and upgrade their room</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9bb099bd-203e-4662-abdc-7b953dc89794">
<p local-id=3D"de926ad69af9"><strong>When</strong> a reservation is created=
 =E2=86=92 <strong>Then</strong> add a note to the guest profile</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7d3aaa7971db">Each automation is built on a visual canvas wh=
ere you drag, drop, and connect components to define your workflow. No codi=
ng or technical skills are required.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b4122f34-1136-4023-80c5-f92d23d5d44f">
<h2 local-id=3D"5b5fb63fab05" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-2.Key=
Concepts">2. Key Concepts</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0762e6a345b4">Before you start building, here are the core c=
oncepts you need to know:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"da=
9ab788-8244-4abe-be58-4484e9b868a9" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b08bb6fa-5032-4636-adaf-6866f0b9fae2">
<th data-local-id=3D"8e474392-89f6-491a-9706-8a12becf8d7f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"44297807fe35">Concept</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"16a1cfe4-dc62-45be-a872-0a56495fc662" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3afa747d59e3">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d3800410-9403-4ba0-bc1b-e50bf2ccaee8">
<td data-local-id=3D"67e2ab3d-59a5-44a7-81cb-bd06380326bd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"38ade6255b8e"><strong>Automation (Flow)</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4e37374c-b7ee-42af-874b-e26d96c44a71" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"31d42aa29f75">A complete workflow that defines a sequence of=
 steps. Each automation has a name, a status (Active or Inactive), and is m=
ade up of connected components.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3dcca2ab-370a-4ef1-aeb0-0c35b5276166">
<td data-local-id=3D"00080cd6-f2c9-4b86-9a78-95dc10af9292" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"574bfdb4a22b"><strong>Trigger</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8e6b5875-8d8c-4748-a146-6888a0017b3e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"331841f505db">The starting point of every automation. A trig=
ger defines <em>when</em> the automation runs. It can be an event (e.g. "Re=
servation Created") or a schedule (e.g. "Every day at 9 AM"). Every automat=
ion must have exactly one trigger.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c4072880-d8b5-4447-8fc3-2a1673655e08">
<td data-local-id=3D"5d341f1f-f316-4661-8ef6-0dca36c0548d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fe8400340c28"><strong>Action</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4ed1096a-adef-4987-9938-457086e8ef75" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dad8c5958784">A step that <em>does</em> something: retrieves=
 data, sends a message, adds a product, creates a task, etc. Actions run in=
 the order they are connected.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"20ef29c2-fab1-4c21-8593-dbe2ffbcbc15">
<td data-local-id=3D"a6001507-cd3d-4cab-8c1a-122d93e365c7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"aef5ec31b7e6"><strong>Component</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6a29c454-a444-462e-a02a-11ea202909d5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a500a15a2ba3">A building block on the canvas. Both triggers =
and actions are components. You configure each component in the Inspector p=
anel.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f9d61a17-9236-4c6d-af48-edb7343a5926">
<td data-local-id=3D"0700bbc9-6c3b-47d0-b473-8692caf4f51c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"52ecc9b96f42"><strong>Connection (Wire)</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c69c575a-f38e-4549-9c14-c3e2786d4c58" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"832222b19200">A line drawn between two components on the can=
vas. It defines the order in which components execute and the flow of data =
between them.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"085c6f23-3783-4e0d-b160-cddc5c37f0ec">
<td data-local-id=3D"e1c4b881-eb16-48ba-8876-fbcd7f3a47e8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c50d1a9c7491"><strong>Variable</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"20e6bc45-fe51-4a4e-8aa5-7de1399191a2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"efe6d1893027">A piece of data output by a component (e.g. a =
guest's name, a reservation ID). You can use variables from earlier compone=
nts as inputs in later ones.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b97f3c14-853f-4da6-b10c-82f366bbaa28">
<td data-local-id=3D"e09094c8-126c-47c9-9588-644dac6c9c44" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c6fefbd189ab"><strong>Modifier</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"059bad1f-015c-4e84-95c5-289e70fac806" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4e09b251a5f7">A built-in transformation you can apply to a v=
ariable =E2=80=94 for example, converting text to uppercase, adding days to=
 a date, or extracting the first item from a list.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"84d98987-91da-4be1-989f-a99e3a03a961">
<td data-local-id=3D"96522e98-f9a2-4463-8adc-e5931bc70e74" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5e9fdf37c0a4"><strong>Inspector</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"86c504a3-b855-4c9d-9fd0-f0e6fbff8393" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"636ee41590cf">The configuration panel that appears on the ri=
ght side of the canvas when you click on a component. This is where you set=
 input values, map variables, and customize behavior.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2f9e92d3-66dd-4308-92c8-2c76e44261fb">
<td data-local-id=3D"9c43130e-ef73-4a48-9861-a551d381d2ce" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ca0979229af9"><strong>Canvas</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"983ee339-9b4d-4a47-86b2-c53630a76872" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"07df467d95d1">The visual workspace where you build your auto=
mation by placing and connecting components.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"8f7dec34-0c0b-46d9-840e-4c36bc49e363">
<h2 local-id=3D"f69540f73af6" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-3.Acc=
essingAutomations">3. Accessing Automations</h2>
<p local-id=3D"cde27b1f8206">To open Automations in Mews:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"beb087ce-2e91-4ab8-975d-35e4fd3a2085">
<li local-id=3D"73894558-dd7a-4994-ac10-3bffd701e054">
<p local-id=3D"71e2e5558993">Log in to your Mews property.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bea3b7a6-de0e-470b-9c90-b93b0cc5ccb3">
<p local-id=3D"80b8e0a57449">Open the <strong>left-hand navigation menu</st=
rong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d6b1b551-bbc0-469d-b1ad-e0c04149eef3">
<p local-id=3D"94f9cfae5146">Click <strong>Settings</strong> to expand the =
section.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4ed3287b-b68d-4c29-bcd9-cc1b0efbf9cd">
<p local-id=3D"572ff043015c">Click <strong>Automations</strong>.</p></li>
</ol><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"image-20260429-130407.png" width=3D"355" loading=3D"lazy"=
 src=3D"ae4c19f0486fe46e5fdc8ec1176c95863128f3619c2d9c07c07d5af9714a40e0" d=
ata-image-src=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19321=
00130/image-20260429-130407.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D17774678=
49393&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1169" data-width=3D=
"355" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"193072=
4140" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attac=
hment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260429-130407.png" dat=
a-base-url=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content=
-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1932100130" data-l=
inked-resource-container-version=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"0feb8309-2129-4794-=
8687-4ee74327527d" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"1167"></span>
<p local-id=3D"8bbbf456e6ef"></p>
<hr local-id=3D"118d1ce1-618f-4104-b1bc-645d65430838">
<h2 local-id=3D"b5be0de642ac" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-4.The=
AutomationsDashboard">4. The Automations Dashboard</h2>
<p local-id=3D"9cd0cdbf6d61">The Automations page is your central hub for m=
anaging all workflows. Here you can see every automation at a glance.</p><s=
pan class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluen=
ce-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-cent=
er" alt=3D"image-20260429-130529.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D=
"30b7665881b3a43e1cf2c0d50717505cd4d19a820d50942e2b789b80ea8e8985" data-ima=
ge-src=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932100130/i=
mage-20260429-130529.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1777467930778&a=
mp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1197" data-width=3D"2228" =
data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1932689652" =
data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment"=
 data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260429-130529.png" data-base=
-url=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=
=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1932100130" data-linked=
-resource-container-version=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"71ba5de3-644f-4345-8364-=
cf8905714fb3" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"251"></span>
<h3 local-id=3D"9b00f9c252b6" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Whaty=
ouseeonthedashboard">What you see on the dashboard</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"5d=
173c64-c029-4286-bc93-40f2ba232374" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"11fb7389-bca5-485d-aa7f-658dd2fe39c2">
<th data-local-id=3D"eadc424a-f4ce-4ec8-ad19-b997b8dd8a7e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6fc36d4a8082">Column</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"5843904a-5491-41e7-82af-94129c281f2a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"90ad6f9bd510">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d7f298d5-59eb-45ae-926a-1ed781ac2f6e">
<td data-local-id=3D"8abaa357-f87c-42d5-91bd-aac47116710b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8e3f9fbac2a1"><strong>Name</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"2220bfac-80af-4e7a-88f5-758c9a481b9f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5fa8a27ff7dc">The name of the automation. Click the pencil i=
con on the right to open and edit it.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c74337f0-9618-4a3b-bbd7-9121d7405b10">
<td data-local-id=3D"c412b9cf-2a62-42e9-90b7-ac24ccde96a8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cd44b4e9f410"><strong>Status</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"00dd48f6-6f3a-47a7-b50e-7fa4ce2f4e01" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8c1fc33fe92f">Shows whether the automation is <strong><span =
data-colorid=3D"k29o33w8yi">Active</span></strong> (running) or <strong>Ina=
ctive</strong> (paused/stopped).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7666ca6e-cb7c-4350-92ea-08e3f30901ab">
<td data-local-id=3D"3bb09f81-3a99-4cd0-98be-da726db954b5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c87137d973b3"><strong>Created</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"18448e23-af95-43cd-b025-33e793d93a81" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f444a53dc53e">The date the automation was first created.</p>=
</td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"713b6259-c715-4365-bc40-70a6944290fa">
<td data-local-id=3D"e9003a23-e5e0-448f-bc62-61b6a7a926eb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6c463c2489b6"><strong>Last modified</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c04c7b26-d94c-47d2-b101-bd746fbad1f4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7eafd1ad9d49">The date the automation was last edited.</p></=
td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7a9c3383-5875-4880-b279-b917622241d3">
<td data-local-id=3D"5f44784e-88b7-4352-88ff-6759af017c1f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6943c5f28286"><strong>Actions</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"afb9cdf1-b79e-4081-9c4b-0d267fd8b6de" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3da96a4940e9">The pencil icon (<strong>Edit</strong>) opens =
the flow designer. The three-dot menu (<strong>More</strong>) provides addi=
tional options such as deactivating or renaming the automation.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"ca3a8e7a7898" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Dashb=
oardfeatures">Dashboard features</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"f34ec487-1b9f-432c-8ba6-be95cf726ddc">
<li local-id=3D"069885e5-0d64-4082-b3eb-aa0ca30c85e9">
<p local-id=3D"b6056e676673"><strong>+ Create button</strong> (top right) =
=E2=80=94 Opens the dialog to create a new automation from scratch or from =
a template.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e9c54dea-e0ff-4af8-8eec-a75438aeaff0">
<p local-id=3D"2e417f5801d8"><strong>Search</strong> =E2=80=94 Filter autom=
ations by name.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6de7fec3-66f2-4d17-a22d-0cbb181a7219">
<p local-id=3D"8559cef44218"><strong>Action log tab</strong> =E2=80=94 Swit=
ch to view a chronological log of all actions executed across your automati=
ons.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"136e7d11-7c20-4512-ba14-e9b80ef4263c">
<h2 local-id=3D"26e5d40f3ca5" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-5.Cre=
atingYourFirstAutomation">5. Creating Your First Automation</h2>
<p local-id=3D"149104dd4663">Click the <strong>+ Create</strong> button in =
the top-right corner of the Automations dashboard. A dialog will appear wit=
h several options:</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image=
-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-e=
mbedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260429-130648.png" width=3D"468"=
 loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"c50c8cfb51e46e63d89a0ffb617a5f89885cc0e312e1ab349d=
a52eaf9ac2b80e" data-image-src=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/download/=
attachments/1932100130/image-20260429-130648.png?version=3D1&amp;modificati=
onDate=3D1777468009709&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"73=
9" data-width=3D"943" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resou=
rce-id=3D"1930887934" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resour=
ce-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260429=
-130648.png" data-base-url=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-=
resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"19=
32100130" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"bb9=
12523-cfe4-40d1-8460-7563a410c272" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"366">=
</span>
<h3 local-id=3D"72c3dd67355e" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Optio=
nA:Startfromatemplate">Option A: Start from a template</h3>
<p local-id=3D"2687b66fc197">Templates are pre-built automations that are n=
early ready to use. Select one and you will get a fully configured flow wit=
h all components already placed and connected. You only need to review the =
settings and adjust any fields specific to your property (such as selecting=
 which products to offer).</p>
<p local-id=3D"bd2858255447">Currently available templates:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"56444e1d-623a-4dda-9703-ea662e3e8a53">
<li local-id=3D"6f893190-f75a-4c29-9257-1308c0f69606">
<p local-id=3D"c0d1ba1ffb0d"><strong>Upgrade room for loyalty members</stro=
ng> =E2=80=94 Automatically upgrades room categories for your loyal guests =
when they arrive, based on availability and occupancy.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"452b9065-b989-4bbd-ac48-8b3a737efcb2">
<p local-id=3D"f4f29a32d83d"><strong>Welcome gift for VIP guests</strong> =
=E2=80=94 Prepares a welcome amenity for VIP guests by creating a task for =
your team and sending the guest an SMS notification.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"902823d77ec4"><strong>Tip:</strong> Templates are the fastes=
t way to get started. Even if the template doesn't match your exact use cas=
e, you can use it as a starting point and customize it to your needs.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"db92ed0e51f8" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Optio=
nB:Customautomation">Option B: Custom automation</h3>
<p local-id=3D"02a8ee21326a">Select <strong>Custom automation</strong> to s=
tart with a blank canvas. You will be taken to the flow designer where you =
can build your workflow from scratch by adding and connecting components.</=
p>
<h3 local-id=3D"c00e10680cc4" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Optio=
nC:Describewhatyouwant(AIprompt)">Option C: Describe what you want (AI prom=
pt)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"dfc074c5c7b8">At the top of the dialog you will see a text f=
ield where you can describe what you want to automate in natural language (=
e.g. <em>"I want to automate how we welcome our VIP guests..."</em>). The s=
ystem will suggest relevant templates or help you get started based on your=
 description.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"0c213c43-2c70-4f54-89b9-f74c04b36bdc">
<h2 local-id=3D"e10dbb044acf" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-6.The=
FlowDesigner(Canvas)">6. The Flow Designer (Canvas)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0938de0f934c">The flow designer is where you visually build =
your automation. It consists of three main areas:</p><span class=3D"conflue=
nce-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-s=
ize"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-202=
60429-130849.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"e86c452ff632b20a306=
a2f269e5b9ccc6b5b91c21caa76a4abcfa63ae15f8b6d" data-image-src=3D"https://me=
ws.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932100130/image-20260429-130849=
.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1777468130873&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&=
amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1071" data-width=3D"2230" data-unresolved-comm=
ent-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1931575993" data-linked-resource=
-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resourc=
e-default-alias=3D"image-20260429-130849.png" data-base-url=3D"https://mews=
.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-l=
inked-resource-container-id=3D"1932100130" data-linked-resource-container-v=
ersion=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"925af917-5dfb-43d8-884c-186abc317ee9" data-me=
dia-type=3D"file" height=3D"224"></span>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"e6=
f68bf6-4bca-4b9d-8736-03c8c5775ec5" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"21debdb4-ffab-4c94-9081-bbef6cd1e04b">
<th data-local-id=3D"f6620bb3-1260-45d0-a236-129fd3d73eb9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"7458dba12011">Area</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"d6044098-b209-4ee9-82de-f9785e1add7e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"9ee9f9f6f53c">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2365c549-ed53-4018-837b-f58b6aa83d06">
<td data-local-id=3D"ddff7cf3-964c-40b5-8017-37c540c963ec" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5429fb2536a4"><strong>Left panel =E2=80=94 Component palette=
</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a235eb72-fe23-4834-97cb-d717c557c032" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6ebb0d7f61d6">A searchable list of all available components =
organized by category. You'll find <strong>Mews</strong> components (trigge=
rs and actions specific to your property) as well as <strong>built-in utili=
ty components</strong> (schedulers, loops, conditions) and <strong>third-pa=
rty integrations</strong>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ccc58135-8d66-4163-a370-8eebeefe94d9">
<td data-local-id=3D"dccb9199-3585-4f24-acda-bbca49dfcb0a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"96874aec3bd8"><strong>Center =E2=80=94 Canvas</strong></p></=
td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3bd0e18e-f6a3-4dbd-96f2-2c81fccc12b0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9e57081d14e8">The main workspace where you place components =
and draw connections between them. You can pan by clicking and dragging the=
 background, and zoom in/out using the scroll wheel or pinch gesture.</p></=
td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"bdfb7767-f66e-4bce-ad9d-a700dc6993fc">
<td data-local-id=3D"4db38b42-c7a2-4059-9415-5eec887ddaee" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"39b5745c1ac4"><strong>Right panel =E2=80=94 Inspector</stron=
g></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"efa4d4f5-545e-4008-8666-48d1f4456b88" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"426745ee60eb">Appears when you click on a component. Shows a=
ll the configuration fields for that component, including input fields, var=
iable mappings, and advanced settings.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"c64215cd3d3b" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Canva=
snavigation">Canvas navigation</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"996a9562-209a-4b81-924b-6ba78771b5c0">
<li local-id=3D"0a0db5c5-2da3-4a7e-96d2-491bf9c9659b">
<p local-id=3D"ddde8127aae9"><strong>Pan:</strong> Click and drag on an emp=
ty area of the canvas to move around.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e88fa174-0c0b-48d2-9213-7f8f7a82c28b">
<p local-id=3D"ec397848f377"><strong>Zoom:</strong> Use the mouse scroll wh=
eel or pinch gesture on a trackpad to zoom in and out.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48465b90-8f57-423c-9f29-2cf7f892c3f5">
<p local-id=3D"9366be4a658e"><strong>Select a component:</strong> Click on =
it. The Inspector panel will open on the right.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fac9d5ed-851c-4170-9cfc-c84b158ff2f8">
<p local-id=3D"b589c7d0c481"><strong>Move a component:</strong> Click and d=
rag the component to reposition it on the canvas.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e086e96d-f065-4ba7-b49c-9a6696b00e52">
<p local-id=3D"000ff7dd8142"><strong>Delete a component:</strong> Select it=
 and press the <code>Delete</code> key, or use the delete option from the c=
omponent's context menu.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"231e0067-a0f4-43cf-a26d-bb3785156226">
<h2 local-id=3D"b38efd442303" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-7.Add=
ingComponentstotheCanvas">7. Adding Components to the Canvas</h2>
<p local-id=3D"93922a09c88d">To add a component to your automation:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8d76aabb-2b19-4f28-a8ee-f7e249feffa6">
<li local-id=3D"8e523386-e6be-4105-8e9b-703a6e070b24">
<p local-id=3D"df740435ad55">Open the <strong>component palette</strong> on=
 the left side of the canvas.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8db82e22-1a9d-4884-86e8-c007894884cd">
<p local-id=3D"dc7e2c3bfa08">Browse the categories or use the <strong>searc=
h bar</strong> to find a specific component.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f2f8c09-e953-48e7-a865-bf8a128600c7">
<p local-id=3D"8e150e23cd5b"><strong>Drag</strong> the component from the p=
alette and <strong>drop</strong> it onto the canvas.</p></li>
</ol><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"image-20260429-130946.png" width=3D"332" loading=3D"lazy"=
 src=3D"70946e67a7de01237bff4d0b1d21a51e26bdd1d25bee5fdcd51695af7548f338" d=
ata-image-src=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19321=
00130/image-20260429-130946.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D17774681=
88076&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1125" data-width=3D=
"332" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"193059=
4562" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attac=
hment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260429-130946.png" dat=
a-base-url=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content=
-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1932100130" data-l=
inked-resource-container-version=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"83e96d15-44c4-41d6-=
a75d-0813fc4c9201" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"1121"></span>
<p local-id=3D"4e954d9163ca">Components are organized into categories:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"bd13aa81-e3ae-4b8d-8c0b-245a6fe0b871">
<li local-id=3D"fa42cb4f-a890-4c65-99e3-568ecf271362">
<p local-id=3D"34231015ad97"><strong>Mews &gt; Triggers</strong> =E2=80=94 =
Event-based starting points (Guest Profile Created, Reservation Created, Re=
servation Checked In).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"72517f40-5fc3-4310-b527-49463fb27abd">
<p local-id=3D"6b8f7fcccc26"><strong>Mews &gt; Actions</strong> =E2=80=94 O=
perations you perform in Mews (Add Note, Send SMS, Upgrade Room, etc.).</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"b783f693-7cf6-4698-824f-dac43d033102">
<p local-id=3D"9ecbbd3b5861"><strong>Utilities</strong> =E2=80=94 Built-in =
components for scheduling, looping, branching, and data manipulation.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"70ee84ce-ed14-4abc-a153-35cfe05e6262">
<p local-id=3D"12402e79193b"><strong>Third-party integrations</strong> =E2=
=80=94 Connect to external services and tools (where available).</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"24a6598df6fe"><strong>Tip:</strong> If you're not sure which=
 component you need, use the search bar at the top of the palette. Typing "=
SMS" will show the Send SMS component; typing "arrivals" will show Get Elig=
ible Arrivals, etc.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"a39e4239-ac8f-48b9-9ebf-492747279fff">
<h2 local-id=3D"65e394be2727" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-8.Con=
nectingComponents">8. Connecting Components</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8d1329632e08">Components on the canvas have <strong>ports</s=
trong> =E2=80=94 small circles on their edges. To create a connection:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"c7cedeb0-d73e-4b6a-941c-afb20e51c181">
<li local-id=3D"2b6c30dd-a02e-417a-bed2-6e262fd55344">
<p local-id=3D"f17cbbc841d8">Hover over the <strong>output port</strong> (r=
ight side) of the source component. The port circle will highlight.</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"1b0f785b-6f4c-4da2-9fcd-6292ef0f5dc4">
<p local-id=3D"da0a9d0e6b61"><strong>Click and drag</strong> from the outpu=
t port to the <strong>input port</strong> (left side) of the target compone=
nt.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e9ce679c-d1b4-4d70-957c-f432e36cb379">
<p local-id=3D"5c43c27b4108">Release the mouse button. A <strong>wire</stro=
ng> (line) will appear connecting the two components.</p></li>
</ol><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"image-20260429-131030.png" width=3D"408" loading=3D"lazy"=
 src=3D"ffc25e509ee282bcde9786b2d576e8009ce53a96a4e6ba0e3aea301fbf2c6ba6" d=
ata-image-src=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19321=
00130/image-20260429-131030.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D17774682=
31500&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"421" data-width=3D"=
408" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1932722=
300" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attach=
ment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260429-131030.png" data=
-base-url=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-=
type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1932100130" data-li=
nked-resource-container-version=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"c8bf9f80-6be1-47c6-a=
fc8-26788ccb874c" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"421"></span>
<p local-id=3D"2e3613a6d9bc"><strong>How connections work:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"b8a147ef-82f7-4fbb-b063-87f61f4cac6f">
<li local-id=3D"09b07446-80cf-4be3-8825-a37dd84a9998">
<p local-id=3D"ee16687c8953">Data flows from <strong>left to right</strong>=
 along the wires. The output of one component becomes available as input to=
 the next.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0c547473-ca5d-4c4d-8f8c-b20b3f557d53">
<p local-id=3D"ea63e3829924">A component can connect to <strong>multiple do=
wnstream</strong> components (branching).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"85b49f62-06c8-4ad7-81c9-454c40d45a6c">
<p local-id=3D"a0f68230f22d">A component can receive connections from <stro=
ng>multiple upstream</strong> components.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4180aa9-3a76-44b0-bc17-f49b5f15190c">
<p local-id=3D"49aea233e5df">To <strong>remove a connection</strong>, click=
 on the wire and press <code>Delete</code>, or right-click and select remov=
e.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4d51b1bb0290">The order of connections determines the execut=
ion order. When a trigger fires, the automation runs through the connected =
components following the wires, from left to right.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"20c729a7-e72b-49c7-afd4-6c9258018ac2">
<h2 local-id=3D"0c178df255a3" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-9.Con=
figuringComponents(theInspector)">9. Configuring Components (the Inspector)=
</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e634c59214a7">Click on any component on the canvas to open t=
he <strong>Inspector panel</strong> on the right side. The Inspector shows =
all the configuration fields for that component.</p><span class=3D"confluen=
ce-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-si=
ze"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-2026=
0429-131108.png" width=3D"407" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"c6d40d7515411ca3d7fd=
97e7c1287ed3dc01ff1aba35ba5b7e7e91b4efa74556" data-image-src=3D"https://mew=
s.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932100130/image-20260429-131108.=
png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1777468270175&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&a=
mp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"744" data-width=3D"407" data-unresolved-comment=
-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1931412258" data-linked-resource-ve=
rsion=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-d=
efault-alias=3D"image-20260429-131108.png" data-base-url=3D"https://mews.at=
lassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-link=
ed-resource-container-id=3D"1932100130" data-linked-resource-container-vers=
ion=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"132f3ec1-71cf-4a71-b6cb-360fa4d6df9f" data-media=
-type=3D"file" height=3D"742"></span>
<h3 local-id=3D"1814de3e05b1" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Field=
typesyouwillencounter">Field types you will encounter</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"3e=
fade7c-8a88-42d0-be62-a3e12bf41776" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c122eb3d-bb62-497d-bba5-267439af4c04">
<th data-local-id=3D"f05402ec-f310-43a7-89f7-08406588242a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5ad7cbb5b504">Field type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"0ab9eb52-8096-4845-9908-ce3dea9f641b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"68c86be5cf76">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3ea14a07-1ae7-470e-9bbb-9af5552762dc">
<td data-local-id=3D"8d2e0610-3224-45ec-a7af-6ae6dc23d17b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8d2eb41ca8aa"><strong>Text input</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e684345b-8681-4350-ad1c-595837ca0b8d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8e27554b0d09">Type a value directly (e.g. a phone number, a =
note message, a cron expression).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6e08f5de-cf1e-4f0a-870a-2cd3fe2e4156">
<td data-local-id=3D"7e74f12b-45f6-4b7c-a5a0-f96018d6cbc3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e489f9b66e4a"><strong>Dropdown</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"6c75acfe-fc8e-47fc-a7a6-f3e20fadabd5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5881f3a14096">Select from a predefined list (e.g. a departme=
nt, a loyalty program, a note classification).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"23ab9b3a-e167-4a43-906b-cdf66ddcb3e2">
<td data-local-id=3D"d53ec61e-f033-4927-ac09-ae7acf53ef46" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3c5ebc5b3471"><strong>Toggle</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"deffd5b5-f5ef-4d0d-85e2-56dd36f1b1d7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d2f22120e4c9">Switch a setting on or off (e.g. "Trigger imme=
diately: True/False").</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"576d02f5-3816-4d8a-86e7-40bdf795a246">
<td data-local-id=3D"283f7216-9cfb-4952-8f8d-67712cfd6290" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a34d8e4e5dd6"><strong>Number input</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"41f2741c-c765-40f8-8c16-cff62cec3059" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9bc7e0093e64">Enter a numeric value (e.g. quantity, buffer t=
hreshold, delay in milliseconds).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2150d8e0-b15c-47f5-bd07-0cccc98a2a51">
<td data-local-id=3D"09f88fb2-a93e-47ad-9a83-2901bec24f76" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0d91ad1c3647"><strong>Variable picker (+)</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dc890b80-0be3-498e-b088-162e263c3686" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cbb3edcb4c49">Click the <strong>+</strong> button next to a =
field to dynamically reference output from a previous component. See <a hre=
f=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/GX/pages/1932100130/Getting+Sta=
rted+with+Mews+Automations#10.-Using-Variables-from-Previous-Components" re=
l=3D"nofollow">Section 10</a>.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"68299919e936">Each field includes a <strong>help text</stron=
g> description below it explaining what the field does and what values are =
accepted.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ec88be7c5884"><strong>Important:</strong> Fields marked as <=
strong>Required</strong> must be filled in before the automation can run. F=
ields marked as Optional have sensible defaults and can be left as-is.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"e4e61d73-99e7-4dcb-a88e-cae98ddeae0e">
<h2 local-id=3D"6b2d2bfbba76" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-10.Us=
ingVariablesfromPreviousComponents">10. Using Variables from Previous Compo=
nents</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c5c8729fefe5">One of the most powerful features of Automatio=
ns is the ability to use the <strong>output of one component as the input f=
or another</strong>. This is how data flows through your automation.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"d7479aa913bc" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Howto=
referenceavariable">How to reference a variable</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ac6a3303-399f-497e-875f-a26fc4c519cd">
<li local-id=3D"7a5f82c3-f4dd-4b20-9836-4b52c30553f4">
<p local-id=3D"b2185c18693d">Click on the component you want to configure.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b553cd3c-4d3a-449d-86e5-c3d4659f8a39">
<p local-id=3D"556cd37d10da">In the Inspector, find the input field where y=
ou want to use data from a previous component.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f5208f00-53c3-49fd-bb76-ecfaa7f8bc5d">
<p local-id=3D"bc9fa6b73dc3">Click the <strong>+ button</strong> next to th=
at field. The <strong>variable picker</strong> will open.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6d54dcb9-861a-4b4e-b1ec-5834b0e95abb">
<p local-id=3D"1373b325f895">You will see a list of all upstream (previous)=
 components and their available output fields.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"060345a4-cdb1-4190-88b7-77f8f8b44df3">
<p local-id=3D"09c92b8b0446">Click on the output field you want to use. It =
will be inserted into the input field as a <strong>variable tag</strong> (a=
 colored pill showing the source component and field name).</p></li>
</ol><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"image-20260429-131205.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy"=
 src=3D"2da3befde017ae71c52b83da153aeca535218e5c3f715ddadb5647b286e6687f" d=
ata-image-src=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19321=
00130/image-20260429-131205.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D17774683=
27317&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"835" data-width=3D"=
775" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1932067=
702" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attach=
ment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260429-131205.png" data=
-base-url=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-=
type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1932100130" data-li=
nked-resource-container-version=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"180f7c95-db3c-42e9-9=
372-1a33dacee629" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"504"></span>
<h3 local-id=3D"6326497bad48" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Examp=
le">Example</h3>
<p local-id=3D"0ca7de71f65a">Say your automation starts with <strong>Get El=
igible Arrivals</strong> (which outputs a list of Reservation IDs) and the =
next component is <strong>Each</strong> (which loops over a list). In the E=
ach component's <strong>Field</strong> input, you click <strong>+</strong> =
and select <strong>Get Eligible Arrivals =E2=86=92 out =E2=86=92 Reservatio=
n IDs</strong>. The Each component now knows which list to iterate over.</p=
>
<p local-id=3D"39bc14acfadd"><strong>How it looks:</strong> Once a variable=
 is mapped, the field displays a colored tag like <code>Reservation IDs []<=
/code> with a small pencil icon to edit or modify it. This tag represents t=
he live data that will be passed at runtime.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ecc78aeb9802">You can combine <strong>static text</strong> w=
ith <strong>variables</strong> in the same field. For example, in an SMS me=
ssage you might type: <code>Welcome to our hotel, </code>and then click <st=
rong>+</strong> to insert the guest's first name variable, resulting in a p=
ersonalized message like <em>"Welcome to our hotel, John!"</em>.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"847197dc-3176-470a-a9cd-732d857b55d0">
<h2 local-id=3D"0d26a809e796" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-11.Mo=
difiers=E2=80=94TransformingData">11. Modifiers =E2=80=94 Transforming Data=
</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3047392033a3">Sometimes the data output by one component isn=
't in the exact format you need for the next component. <strong>Modifiers</=
strong> let you transform variables before passing them along =E2=80=94 for=
 example, converting text to uppercase, adding days to a date, or extractin=
g the first item from a list.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"850b0442b01a" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Howto=
applyamodifier">How to apply a modifier</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"29e36f6f-a602-4162-913d-e1608436d037">
<li local-id=3D"1c6fc025-f40b-4d4f-86fb-433825b38cd3">
<p local-id=3D"f99223015961">Click the <strong>pencil icon</strong> on a va=
riable tag in an input field (or click the variable when adding it from the=
 picker).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a573e7af-529b-4500-9eaa-7bb7bbe47ec3">
<p local-id=3D"0d67a53649cd">The <strong>Modify variable</strong> panel ope=
ns, showing:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"216b49bc-b4ed-46f5-a801-86d69f2d9c44">
<li local-id=3D"1289064c-ccd5-4052-9007-eb6a4ba1e81e">
<p local-id=3D"5e6eb0b6faf8"><strong>Left:</strong> The current variable be=
ing modified.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4ce406c-8453-4786-bd45-1e63187a1dae">
<p local-id=3D"1a3db7a45835"><strong>Center:</strong> The list of available=
 modifiers, organized by category.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"539c554f-3ad4-4d56-bbf5-4db9f1b17f17">
<p local-id=3D"7a136aebdc1f"><strong>Right:</strong> A <strong>Test your mo=
difier</strong> panel where you can enter a sample value and see the output=
.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ec73307-e3c9-4f2b-bb3d-a54f7a6cc1f4">
<p local-id=3D"2bb7df3b30fa">Click <strong>Add modifier</strong> and select=
 the transformation you need.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"25731032-ee4e-402f-84fe-c3cb5df19df4">
<p local-id=3D"09dcff0a195c">Modifiers are applied <strong>sequentially</st=
rong> =E2=80=94 you can chain multiple modifiers, and each one transforms t=
he output of the previous one.</p></li>
</ol><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image ima=
ge-center" alt=3D"image-20260429-131228.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy"=
 src=3D"cbf1cbec73ee820b4805402cdc2539514935f00ebc8ecd325b133ef549fea92f" d=
ata-image-src=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19321=
00130/image-20260429-131228.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D17774683=
49521&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"873" data-width=3D"=
1231" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"193298=
4386" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attac=
hment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260429-131228.png" dat=
a-base-url=3D"https://mews.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content=
-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1932100130" data-l=
inked-resource-container-version=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"755bd54d-c184-463e-=
8ace-9a909238825f" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"331"></span>
<h3 local-id=3D"ddc8b9edf9cd" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Modif=
iercategories">Modifier categories</h3>
<p local-id=3D"03602a9b364b">Modifiers are organized into six categories:</=
p>
<h4 local-id=3D"b8c6021bfb27" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Objec=
tmodifiers">Object modifiers</h4>
<p local-id=3D"4f479e84e6be">For working with JSON objects and structured d=
ata.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"cd=
8ea542-9224-491c-8aaa-6de9b9c1f74b" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1cf6cd0d-93c1-4559-ab11-6904de95ea4f">
<th data-local-id=3D"e26c9906-5baf-438c-b25e-a749ea33379d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f810a2a397a7">Modifier</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"e1987d58-4685-436f-b787-ba5cf173f2bf" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d513178c4d07">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"677daac9-3f75-4da6-b26d-a588474a7c4c">
<td data-local-id=3D"8811fa9a-2ae3-40eb-a868-55f5e6213da4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8ad8f06535d5"><strong>Each</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ff4a6042-6a20-4254-8893-262dd470fca2" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5daa30414836">Loop over all values of a list or an object.</=
p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"26d6c53a-b79b-468b-9354-2937036833d1">
<td data-local-id=3D"49bfa886-ba05-4d4a-a181-0ad77bf6d7bb" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
