<h4 local-id=3D"b047a1260d20" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Datem=
odifiers">Date modifiers</h4>
<p local-id=3D"cb48ab50f6a1">For working with dates and times.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"0d=
b2f1a5-eea3-4258-ad75-7195aa91102b" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6bf36ca3-b245-4f67-8519-cac6afe81edc">
<th data-local-id=3D"986caf54-c43c-4713-862b-59255bfb6f6c" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"713357a21aeb">Modifier</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"8260199d-b459-4ff3-a701-ab27e168f278" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"0af6ac7666a6">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8793fc35-e849-473a-8796-5f159f67a51c">
<td data-local-id=3D"c9650223-858b-4950-b37a-fbcfd521ebb4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"15ce135f62f5"><strong>Add Time</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9977e252-209c-4c46-8e22-051a0f53e207" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f31ea0c8a54e">Add a duration to a date (e.g. add 3 days, add=
 2 hours). Useful for setting deadlines or future dates.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"12e94cb8-9eec-4a72-a5a4-87a06d74efb0">
<td data-local-id=3D"b8384cbc-359c-44c4-a523-bfab25e41ef3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6467215792d1"><strong>Subtract Time</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e8f93f40-2a67-43bd-8a13-8be67a348cf0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"30e257ad762a">Subtract a duration from a date (e.g. go back =
1 week).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"38da98d8-69e1-4f6d-ac91-e6d6492f0fc0">
<td data-local-id=3D"8fa92970-06b9-469d-9d08-7b20fc91c432" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"88ee66797cde"><strong>Format Date</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c6b30159-7c4c-461e-80d1-73d69ab23a16" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bd3d69221cbc">Format a date into a specific display format (=
e.g. <code>DD/MM/YYYY</code>, <code>MMMM Do, YYYY</code>).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5bbfdbf7-a5ea-4c69-8370-c0a016ec00eb">
<td data-local-id=3D"c4150113-e7e6-47f4-9d6e-2d68eb1aca7e" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"acbca0f2545d"><strong>Now</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9d9e86d8-72de-4db8-a5b4-792ec5d5781f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"82df771d177c">Return the current date and time.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"cbf36b6e-0b7e-49d5-98f7-910154ab91fa">
<td data-local-id=3D"9f75fc32-cff5-4cfd-8333-bc4ac11f0345" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a274fb509230"><strong>Parse Date</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"01f27ff8-4b7e-441b-acd9-5cb9f31ffb99" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f9d286f06141">Convert a text string into a date object using=
 a specified format.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c42239dc-cbec-4903-9823-f944d3fb6d7b">
<td data-local-id=3D"cf8cf3b2-0c2a-430d-aa73-ee6e00e9b245" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"28bc99f04b87"><strong>Difference</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4b753995-bc95-46ef-8c47-5ca889558acd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9c70ccf8e3b6">Calculate the difference between two dates (in=
 days, hours, minutes, etc.).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c88cc83f-f5f1-4a9b-9528-057bef857cd9">
<td data-local-id=3D"716b0fa4-7dfb-4c3d-8d99-3dd56ef54521" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9db7a03f676e"><strong>Start Of</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d51516a4-0da7-42ed-ba82-e1d54d144af0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"05dd11f5ea30">Get the start of a time period (e.g. start of =
the day, start of the month).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5f21fc24-0865-43d2-a656-642866e1e14e">
<td data-local-id=3D"5c31a64e-e68f-42be-a697-b06669ced8a8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7a88bc0d3789"><strong>End Of</strong></p></td>
