</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"b7c37639e1b2" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Testi=
ngmodifiers">Testing modifiers</h3>
<p local-id=3D"89b2d394963f">The <strong>Test your modifier</strong> panel =
(on the right side of the Modify variable screen) lets you enter a sample i=
nput value and click <strong>Test</strong> to see the output. This is an ex=
cellent way to verify your transformations before running the automation.</=
p>
<p local-id=3D"df145f81a8d0"><strong>Tip:</strong> You can chain multiple m=
odifiers. For example, to get tomorrow's date formatted nicely: start with =
a date variable =E2=86=92 apply <strong>Add Time</strong> (+1 day) =E2=86=
=92 apply <strong>Format Date</strong> (DD/MM/YYYY). Each modifier processe=
s the output of the previous one.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"404032c0-7d5c-463e-808e-395d9327b37d">
<h2 local-id=3D"c27e85a35802" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-12.Me=
wsComponentsOverview">12. Mews Components Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"7aec2418d085">Mews provides its own set of components design=
ed specifically for hospitality workflows. These are grouped into <strong>T=
riggers</strong> and <strong>Actions</strong>.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"64c2ac77e818" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Trigg=
ers(event-based)">Triggers (event-based)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8f135885c771">Triggers start your automation when something =
happens in Mews.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"bf=
4d22eb-7c5a-44ad-bac3-62f5e851f992" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c1355851-1671-44af-8a4c-d30bc84748d4">
<th data-local-id=3D"4ad99086-b0c3-41ae-91a8-6e1bc87d0c28" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d108bb29b493">Trigger</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"c17a2dc6-9695-4a18-9aa9-418e60c9a24a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c06adce0ece2">When it fires</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"09e7c34d-74f7-4476-aa69-b224422ca509" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1f06697de141">Key output data</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"fc74f372-c8d4-4513-86b7-7fa1b1b3da68">
<td data-local-id=3D"dec2d352-3d12-4056-9f18-b9107b108a61" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d98c2211ed85"><strong>Guest Profile Created</strong></p></td=
>
<td data-local-id=3D"832d46bc-2bd0-4887-a79f-d701779757a8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"13b70cb235fd">A new guest profile is added to Mews.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a1e2fe3a-bcd7-4e0c-8f6c-486ba1267168" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"198fa7fbbc43">Guest name, email, phone, nationality, languag=
e, loyalty code.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"17708851-4b41-419e-9357-1ed8517baaaa">
<td data-local-id=3D"2e9e5a7d-1254-451f-a2e1-e5b5e1b10fd3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"26535cc954d4"><strong>Reservation Created</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ad7eacba-cd19-46ca-bf71-7537fc4171c7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8ff10de0ee63">A new reservation is created.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"a245c41b-9217-43c7-991a-316e942a052f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"308e50b0a3f5">Reservation ID, confirmation number, guest det=
ails, origin, assigned space, rate, dates.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f85e198f-ee54-41a4-aca8-adc331327e0f">
<td data-local-id=3D"342da4fe-01ca-4048-a434-8e0b32877b6f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cb4f1da1530e"><strong>Reservation Checked In</strong></p></t=
d>
<td data-local-id=3D"1de654b7-168c-46f3-ad2d-1e68f99a4d28" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c5ca80f584e6">A guest checks in at the property.</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"35e5948f-cefc-4df9-b000-57700d610118" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fef5dee4ee46">Reservation ID, guest details, room assignment=
, check-in/out dates.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 local-id=3D"e7b0ba70d977" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Actio=
ns(operations)">Actions (operations)</h3>
<h4 local-id=3D"d4d296d6a937" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-Guest=
&amp;ReservationOperations">Guest &amp; Reservation Operations</h4>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"59=
ae5c74-ba27-4dad-a694-614cc47c0be2" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ad098f2f-9455-452a-9026-fee055797671">
<th data-local-id=3D"815986a7-56f4-40ba-842c-f12ce956addc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5eb0dd5cfb8a">Action</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"69108851-54c6-4de4-8caf-177b142cbffe" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c3a3d33c73b0">What it does</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b1bf67f4-af6f-4909-9d07-b16c9149b736">
<td data-local-id=3D"7dc1caa0-3021-4102-9a72-ed1780cf5bed" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"080a3607a238"><strong>Add Note to Guest Profile</strong></p>=
</td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e0502203-add9-4eaa-b1f5-5e88e52eaf3f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a1c6b3ada6a6">Adds a categorized text note (e.g. Housekeepin=
g, Complaints, Compliments) to a guest's profile.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"bcf02341-867b-41f6-a7df-a702034b3907">
<td data-local-id=3D"3d911fb8-026e-4d2a-82d9-5a2e51e22ed8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"696f3995a97f"><strong>Add Note to Reservation</strong></p></=
td>
<td data-local-id=3D"671cf976-fe27-4b1d-844f-e1ad4d6ac2ab" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ecc90ab8f8a4">Adds a note to one or more reservations, usefu=
l for group bookings or operational remarks.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"833bce84-6eb1-412d-b9d2-adc7aa95a0a7">
<td data-local-id=3D"3249417a-449d-4cba-8040-6b21de9bfda9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d58ff8f28993"><strong>Add Product to Reservation</strong></p=
></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4188bcfe-3542-4e64-b316-7b7df0489de9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"863e95591f09">Adds a product or charge (e.g. breakfast, park=
ing, late checkout) to a reservation with configurable quantity and date ra=
nge.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c7e948f7-021b-48a6-8da6-0edff32c08bb">
<td data-local-id=3D"95ba80c4-8494-491f-bced-8ecd684a621f" class=3D"conflue=
