nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"77afc8ff76e3">Upgrades a guest to a higher room category bas=
ed on configurable upgrade paths, availability, and buffer settings.</p></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b60bd050-39da-4d25-a6ad-98625678a75d">
<td data-local-id=3D"1546ab80-d850-4ed4-ba60-cf01e1076079" class=3D"conflue=
