<p local-id=3D"af4add9aa282"><strong>Note:</strong> For detailed documentat=
ion of each component =E2=80=94 including every input field, output field, =
and step-by-step behavior =E2=80=94 see the individual component documentat=
ion pages.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"943dc9bb-a707-4a4b-aed4-dc7fb5b064df">
<h2 local-id=3D"f8323c710998" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-13.Bu=
ilt-inUtilityComponents">13. Built-in Utility Components</h2>
<p local-id=3D"bcf653b44981">In addition to Mews-specific components, the a=
utomation platform provides a set of <strong>built-in utility components</s=
trong> that help you control how your workflow behaves. These are essential=
 building blocks for any automation.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"4ca0e6af2a52" id=3D"GettingStartedwithMewsAutomations-CronS=
cheduler=E2=80=94trigger">Cron Scheduler =E2=80=94 trigger</h3>
<p local-id=3D"1dcfb779a6e0">The <strong>Cron Scheduler</strong> triggers y=
our automation on a recurring schedule using cron syntax. Use it when you w=
ant your automation to run at specific times (e.g. every morning at 9 AM, e=
very Monday, on the first of each month).</p><span class=3D"confluence-embe=
dded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><im=
g class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260429-13=
2301.png" width=3D"419" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"3f9386c65ec306516d9407ba3d8=
7a08375d9beb62b68f49712be4196c8ac6bc6" data-image-src=3D"https://mews.atlas=
sian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932100130/image-20260429-132301.png?ver=
sion=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1777468984227&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=
=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1069" data-width=3D"419" data-unresolved-comment-coun=
t=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1932296657" data-linked-resource-version=
=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-defaul=
t-alias=3D"image-20260429-132301.png" data-base-url=3D"https://mews.atlassi=
an.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-re=
source-container-id=3D"1932100130" data-linked-resource-container-version=
=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"ea50f262-9377-441d-863e-59d84de1b8d8" data-media-ty=
pe=3D"file" height=3D"1068"></span>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"d6=
4fec0d-05eb-4c0a-86fc-f494b3a73a78" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c11c52d6-5b12-4496-816e-39debe1fe40a">
<th data-local-id=3D"2ace33bf-719a-4c61-9eac-d0d24696ae91" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
